{"tid":843860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★高鐵通車旅客圓方　 居民：超市不再賣日用品","createTime":"2018-10-01T12:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:20:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":295,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d77ef062fb9ea6daa47b83845537fc8328dfea","tid":843860,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"自高鐵香港段通車後，附近商場圓方亦多了旅客到訪，出現人山人海的狀況。適逢今日(1日)是十一黃金周首天，圓方內更是人頭湧湧、水泄不通。<br />\n<br />\n有居民感嘆指，高鐵通車後，超市賣的產品與以往有所不同，「現在賣遊客貨、化妝品，少了日常用品！」他並指超市都大排長龍，致使他要花多10數分鐘來回到佐敦購物。<br />\n<br />\n有遊客稱因高鐵才首次來到圓方購物，亦有香港人指因想參觀高鐵站，才特意前來圓方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1924164/org/4f3ba0ed7cec3b0d41831726979726b5.jpg/QX6Ds0akmUSPQJv2Lz5S0Pol8cg3sOWj1gZ9o9YGfaM?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1924164%2Forg%2F4f3ba0ed7cec3b0d41831726979726b5.jpg%2FQX6Ds0akmUSPQJv2Lz5S0Pol8cg3sOWj1gZ9o9YGfaM%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=d2bd95d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地長假期首天，圓方熱鬧非常，到處可見拖篋旅客，附近居民李先生指，自高鐵通車後人流大增，今天更比往常多一倍，「以前不見人堆，現在就有。」他又說，現在超市人頭湧湧，大排長龍，銷售產品類型亦有所改變，「現在賣遊客貨、化妝品，少了大眾化的日常用品！」他稱只可花多幾分鐘，走到佐敦購物。<br />\n<br />\n而住港島的袁女士指，平常很少到圓方，今天是因想參觀高鐵站而到訪，「以前又怎會來？想來參鐵站，未來坐高鐵就可知怎樣走。」她認為圓方屬高消費，不計劃購物，但裝飾精美，空間寬廣。<br />\n<br />\n來自珠海的陳小姐就表示，以前有聽過圓方這個商場，但從未來過，今次因為剛坐完高鐵，而高鐵站正連接住圓方，感覺方便。她指打算在圓方逛街購物，認為圓方品牌齊全，預計會花6000元買衣服及化妝品。<br />\n<br />\n而來自深圳、在圓方等待朋友的郭先生就稱日後必會選擇高鐵，「今天不記得可以坐高鐵，以後會坐，回程搶到票的話也會坐，因為很快，15分鐘就到家，不像以前花1個多小時。」他認為圓方品牌齊全，或會花數千元買衣服。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/241883/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%91%A8-%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%9C%93%E6%96%B9-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91-%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%B3%A3%E6%97%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F241883%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2591%25A8-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%259C%2593%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2593%2581&d=m8n7cz04MUL%2Fdn9A8tPdMb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=54be00c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/241883/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%91%A8-%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%9C%93%E6%96%B9-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91-%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%B3%A3%E6%97%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81</a>"},{"pid":"a4f3e45f883c23771ffd15eceafce50cb4df27b2","tid":843860,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35173a905f4bbd89cb3c836d1da433c7dc96fef6","tid":843860,"uid":35430,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc19cae76add78deaffa6491b73032216e71c3b6","tid":843860,"uid":45760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cf2e85e039689e13d4c52f73003aab9b4c104c","tid":843860,"uid":49730,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:09:20.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"